The evidence with the title 'Court-martialed for sharing religious faith? - FactCheck.org ' says May 10, 2013  ... A post on Examiner.com followed with “ the Obama administration has released a statement confirming the unthinkable : Any soldier who professes Christianity can now be court-martialed and may face imprisonment and a dishonorable discharge from the military … even if they are a military chaplain.” . 
